com.facebook.buck.core.parser

Class BuildTargetPatternToBuildPackagePathComputation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.core.parser.BuildTargetPatternToBuildPackagePathComputation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GraphComputation<BuildTargetPatternToBuildPackagePathKey,BuildPackagePaths>

    public class BuildTargetPatternToBuildPackagePathComputation
extends Object
implements GraphComputation<BuildTargetPatternToBuildPackagePathKey,BuildPackagePaths>
    Discover paths for packages which contain targets that match specification (build target pattern)

    This computation depends on ImmutableFileTreeKey (FileTreeComputation) and ImmutableDirectoryListKey (DirectoryListComputation).

    See WatchmanBuildPackageComputation for an equivalent computation which uses Watchman.
